    public class MyCalendarView
extends com.calendarfx.view.CalendarView
    MyCalendarView class extends the Calendar FX's CalendarView class. Used for getting the calendar view to the application. First day of week is set depending on the chosen language of the application. The calendar view gets the calendar sources from the CalendarController.

      • getMyCalendarView

        public com.calendarfx.view.CalendarView getMyCalendarView()
        Method that creates and returns a CalendarView - a full calendar view with multiple pages for displaying a single day, a week,a month, and an entire year. CalendarSources are taken from the CalendarController. Dapanding of the current locale, weeks start from Monday or Sunday.
        Returns:
        CalendarView a full calendar view with multiple pages
